                            <comment id="14473138" author="melix" created="Wed, 22 Aug 2012 07:53:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Interesting. However, you don&apos;t have to put both annotations. &lt;tt&gt;@CompileStatic&lt;/tt&gt; alone does all the &lt;tt&gt;@TypeChecked&lt;/tt&gt; job plus static compilation.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14473095" author="imi" created="Wed, 22 Aug 2012 08:02:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;yeah, I know I don&apos;t need to put both. I just thought I would report it as &quot;minor&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
